text: The OSIRIS-REx spacecraft has successfully stowed the sample collector head, which is full of surface material gathered from near-Earth asteroid Bennu, in the sample return capsule. This will prevent any more of the sample from leaking into space. https://t.co/VQU2qgGEIr

name: CNN
text: The Trump administration is dropping the gray wolf from the endangered species list under the assertion that the animal's population has sufficiently recovered, a move conservation groups decry as shortsighted and promise to challenge in court https://t.co/8NglqMUVMY

name: CNN
text:
In transcripts of a 1971 conversation with Bob Dylan that are going up for auction, the song "Lay Lady Lay" is revealed to have been written for Barbra Streisand.

In a March interview, it's clear Dylan wrote the song for her, not necessarily about her. https://t.co/RVLcARNPVV

text: The 8th US Circuit Court of Appeals has ruled that mailed-in ballots in Minnesota must be received by elections officials no later than Election Day https://t.co/UAWTGCD2os
